comments.content: Looks like an advanced version of [Danube](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419133846/http:/www.dafont.com/danube.font?text=abcdp) by No Image Fonts. Freeware.

My guess would be [Rezland](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419133846/http:/www.dafont.com/font.php?file=rezland&page=1&nb_ppp_old=50&text=abcdpq&nb_ppp=50&psize=l&classt=alpha) with obvious work done to round off the ends.
